{"tid":2202440,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"論時間劇 冇一套夠\"命運石之門\"講得好","createTime":"2020-09-14T14:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T01:50:44.000Z","uid":40494,"like":21,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c0538dc11bd32b37e4d7a549927e04e2ed34a84d","tid":2202440,"uid":40494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都睇咗好多套有關時間既劇<br />\n最近熱門既Dark, Tenet 都有睇<br />\n我更加肯定命運石之門一定係當中最好既一套<br />\n強勁既劇情震撼力，同時喺神展開同埋伏筆回收兩方面做到&ldquo;登峰造極&rdquo;既地步<br />\n故事線完整，邏輯嚴密<br />\n好多入面既嘢都係參考返現實同樣存在既嘢<br />\n最重要係個結局係極之合理，唔會加插啲無謂既設定<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"b66e7a0175ef34618d47e2dde057f4a2f895bd88","tid":2202440,"uid":15603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"唔記得晒講乜<br />\n有冇人有懶人包"},{"pid":"601baee7021f831b390a91aca26226a83490cd09","tid":2202440,"uid":46840,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"雖然冇睇內文UP乜鳩<br />\n但係見到不服來辯就好撚扯火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbae0586e37ba0f20297b0904bce451d0804255","tid":2202440,"uid":40494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce02e1eacd5e2d95439b561c50ef7cef461ee70b","tid":2202440,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"吓？<br />\n咁垃圾都好睇？"},{"pid":"c7efaab3ea247eef331ca55b74c1623dc1181f04","tid":2202440,"uid":40494,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7gJLt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7gJLt8.png&h=d094ae50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38b175b66466c391c97e90d2cf9e97484b24eeab","tid":2202440,"uid":40494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"比返啲有質素既反駁既唔該"},{"pid":"5a608651da7819f2e4a0f26be28e6255cdbb9071","tid":2202440,"uid":240733,"like":0,"dislike":